kind: str\n    encrypted: bool\n    authenticated: bool\n\n\ndef find_earliest_available_slot(\n    existing_slots: list[Slot],\n    reference_time: int = 0,\n    slot_duration: int =
SLOT_DURATION_MINUTES,\n    gap: int = GAP_MINUTES,\n) -> int:\n    """Find the earliest available time slot respecting gaps.\n\n    Args:\n        existing_slots: List of existing 
