  ### 1. Task outcome (short version):                                                                                                                                                 
  Successfully built and verified a complete Apple-inspired React/TypeScript (Vite) frontend for the Airport Runway Scheduling System (project 7). All 7 user stories (tasks 46-52)    
  are covered across 6 pages with a shared Layout and navigation. The TypeScript build compiles cleanly. All 7 test suites pass (7/7 passed).                                          
                                                                                                                                                                                       
  ### 2. Task outcome (extremely detailed version):                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                       
  **Backend Verification:**                                                                                                                                                            
  - Backend fully implemented (0 unimplemented stubs, 123 source files)                                                                                                                
  - 62 mounted API routes across 15 resource routers (flights, slots, runways, emergency_flights, separation_rules, traffic_datas, aircrafts, interfaces, operations,                  
  operation_slots, states, resources, permissions, health)                                                                                                                             
  - 39 Pydantic DTO schemas mapped to TypeScript interfaces                                                                                                                            
                                                                                                                                                                                       
  **Frontend Implementation:**                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                                                       
  **Feature Groups and Pages Created:**                                                                                                                                                
  1. **Dashboard (HomePage)** — `/` route — shows counts of flights, runways, and slots with styled cards                                                                              
  2. **Flight Registration (FlightsPage)** — `/flights` — register new flights (flightNumber + aircraftType), view aircraft movement log, delete flights                               
  3. **Slot Allocation (SlotsPage)** — `/slots` — create new time slots, view all slots with availability status and time display                                                      
  4. **Runway Management (RunwaysPage)** — `/runways` — add runways (capacity + configuration), delete runways, close runways (sets capacity to 0), view runway timetables per runway  
  with flight details and status                                                                                                                                                       
  5. **Emergency Flight Handling (EmergencyFlightsPage)** — `/emergency` — select a flight and allocate it the next available slot, displays available slots and registered flights    
  6. **Timetable (TimetablePage)** — `/timetable` — select a runway to view its full slot timetable including flight numbers, aircraft types, and statuses                             
                                                                                                                                                                                       
  **Core Files Created (15 total):**                                                                                                                                                   
  - `src/types/index.ts` — 26 TypeScript interfaces matching backend DTOs                                                                                                              
  - `src/api/services.ts` — 49 axios API calls covering all backend endpoints                                                                                                          
  - `src/components/Layout.tsx` — shared navigation with 6 links + Outlet                                                                                                              
  - `src/pages/HomePage.tsx` — dashboard with stat cards                                                                                                                               
  - `src/pages/FlightsPage.tsx` — flight registration with CRUD                                                                                                                        
  - `src/pages/SlotsPage.tsx` — slot management                                                                                                                                        
  - `src/pages/RunwaysPage.tsx` — runway CRUD, closures, timetables                                                                                                                    
  - `src/pages/EmergencyFlightsPage.tsx` — emergency handling UI                                                                                                                       
  - `src/pages/TimetablePage.tsx` — runway timetable viewer                                                                                                                            
  - `src/App.tsx` — updated with all routes + Layout wrapper                                                                                                                           
  - `src/__tests__/HomePage.test.tsx` + `FlightsPage.test.tsx` + `SlotsPage.test.tsx` + `RunwaysPage.test.tsx` + `EmergencyFlightsPage.test.tsx` + `TimetablePage.test.tsx`            
                                                                                                                                                                                       
  **Static Analysis & Auto-Fixes Applied:**                                                                                                                                            
  - `verify_package_json_deps` — OK (no misclassified packages)                                                                                                                        
